POA/HSEQ-POL/001 
 
HEALTH, SAFETY, SECURITY & ENVIRONMENT POLICY 
It is our objective to carry out all our operations with the greatest regard for the health and 
safety of all workers and conserving the environment.  
  
Management believes that safety and efficient production go hand-in-hand.   
  
Every  effort  is  made  to  prevent  injury  to  our  employees  by  taking  all  possible  steps  to 
improve working conditions and practices.   
  
In  order  to  ensure  the  safety  of  our  workers,  the  company  has  developed  a  health  and 
safety program manual with company policies and procedures that everyone must follow at 
all times. To enforce these procedures, management makes routine checks of the work site.  
  
In this regard, our policy statement is;  
 To protect and conserve the environment when carrying out our activities. 
 To provide safe working conditions to our staff and the public. 
 To keep our staff in a health condition. 
 To ensure our activities do not harm the society.  
  
Primax Outdoor Advertising functions in line with all  generally acceptable laws, codes and 
standards applying to operations to ensure the safety and protection of all those working in 
our operations.  
  
 All workers are also expected to comply with the law and company job requirements. Our 
incident   prevention   program   has   the   co-operative   efforts   of   both   the   workers   and 
management  in  order  to  be  successful.  Everyone  helps  in  recognizing  and  eliminating 
hazards as they are found. With the daily commitment and support of everybody, we work 
together as a team to reduce job hazards and maintain an efficient and safe operation. 
 
 
 
HUZAIR MUKALAZI 10
th
 January 2026 
