POA/HSEQ-POL/002 
ENVIROMENTAL POLICY 
PRIMAX OUTDOOR ADVERTISING is committed to; 
1. Operating in a manner that protects the environment. 
 
2. Being efficient in the use of material and limited energy resources by minimizing waste 
through re-use, recovery or recycling where feasible in our operations and projects. 
 
3. Influencing our employees, suppliers and business stakeholder to share the same 
commitment toward environmental conservation and protection. 
 
Our policy is to: 
 Identify all potential environmental impacts that our company contributes to and 
establish appropriate mitigating measure. 
 
 Set and adopt environmental protection targets, monitor our environmental 
performance and take action in order improve as may be necessary. 
 
 Assign responsibility for environmental matters at all appropriate levels in the company 
to ensure accountability. 
 
 Provide follow-up programs that verify the accuracy of the environmental assessments 
and the effectiveness of the mitigation measures. 
 
 Use products and work methods that have minimal or no impact on the environment. 
 
 
 
